- Brands: Tier 1 (Fender, Gibson, Martin), Tier 2 (Ibanez, ESP), etc.
- Types: Electric, Acoustic, Classical, Bass, Hollow-body, Semi-hollow
- Conditions: Mint, Excellent, Very Good, Good, Fair, Poor, For Parts
- Key specs: Body material, neck material, pickup configuration, year
- German market: Focus on European brands and local preferences
```

### German Market Context
```
For German market features, consider:
- Language: German primary, English secondary
- Currency: EUR only
- Payments: SEPA, PayPal, Klarna popular
- Shipping: DHL, Hermes, DPD common carriers
- Legal: GDPR compliance, German consumer protection laws
- Culture: Quality over quantity, detailed descriptions expected
```

### Security Context
